ActNational Energy Board Act
PrecisAppointment of GAÉTAN CARON of Calgary, Alberta, Chairman of the National Energy Board for a term ending on June 8, 2014; and reappointment of GAÉTAN CARON as a member of the National Energy Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years, effective June 9, 2010.
